{"tid":1389301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全民運動月,有片]斯文靚仔教劍擊","createTime":"2019-07-31T01:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:57.000Z","uid":215715,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4eb8d8e146c758845ca7ce06f84a5307a7fef8b2","tid":1389301,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:10:09.000Z","msg":"劍擊，在廣義上講是指<span style=\"color: red;\">用手持兵器刺、戳的技術。</span>現代一般多作為擊劍體育項目的代名詞，是一種格鬥運動，這裡指的擊劍（Fencing）是以17世紀後單手用的護手刺劍為主的格鬥運動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記撚住係刺，斬係冇撚用架</span><br />\n<br />\n劍擊點樣進攻<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NItdl7W23-s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNItdl7W23-s&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=a982f50b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NItdl7W23-s</a><br />\n<br />\n搶攻方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7Xr0HB2V9G4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Xr0HB2V9G4&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=8abc68e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Xr0HB2V9G4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qZ35H0_nnc8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqZ35H0_nnc8&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=3729c434\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qZ35H0_nnc8</a><br />\n<br />\n點樣擊中對方既手<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9Psn3EhCnVA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9Psn3EhCnVA&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=ff4fc37f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9Psn3EhCnVA</a><br />\n<br />\n點該你班廢青做多d運動<br />\n唔好成日諗住恰鳩d差佬<br />\n做多d運動就可以保護我地尊敬既警察叔叔安安全全咁番屋企 一家齊齊整整 <br />\n老婆仔女就唔洗擔心佢地點解咁夜都唔番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZAEv6c0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZAEv6c0.gif&h=92d2288b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"524fb48a0cb139528145e53bf8cdbdac0eacb849","tid":1389301,"uid":270378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"正式既進攻動作係要先手後出腳移動<br />\n因為咁係會無咁痛架<br />\n我試過比人手腳同時出咁刺<br />\n真係會痛到痴線架<br />\n大家千奇唔好咁做"},{"pid":"2db9d06e442a2f6839bfa8577d628394d38f8e7d","tid":1389301,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"8月5"},{"pid":"d40cdb2ccb83cb81aaef0a3cfe494fa9bdc5b5e8","tid":1389301,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ac13c68b7ada76da3c264ab0a91a8ba5cd135d","tid":1389301,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T21:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dbf3233e8912f0be8ce62bc41f67b056411003","tid":1389301,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}